  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to embark on a new journey, test your reflexes and climb the levels! In this fast-paced survival game, you control a glowing orb, navigating through a mysterious, ever-changing world filled with <strong>dangerous obstacles and relentless enemies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/00d86eee174ba22688c692ca9c52691f.avif?t=1774464132\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🚀 A Thrilling and Evolving Challenge</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level is a challenge to the exit portal, but reaching it won’t be easy! Collect XP orbs to level up and choose from <strong>powerful upgrades</strong>, including passive boosts and unique spells to enhance your survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/901c2df80938f68096e3f8ae970ecaed.poster.avif?t=1774464132\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/901c2df80938f68096e3f8ae970ecaed.webm?t=1774464132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/901c2df80938f68096e3f8ae970ecaed.mp4?t=1774464132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚡ No Attacks, Only Pure Evasion</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There’s no fighting back, only your skills and instincts will keep you alive! The further you go, the <strong>tougher the enemies, the trickier the paths, and the faster your decisions must be</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/eb6ca740d3e97bf26082cc58106b9e6a.poster.avif?t=1774464132\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/eb6ca740d3e97bf26082cc58106b9e6a.webm?t=1774464132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/eb6ca740d3e97bf26082cc58106b9e6a.mp4?t=1774464132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌍 Explore Unique Biomes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your journey will take you through <strong>multiple mysterious biomes</strong>, each with its own atmosphere and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/c7128b21159c98a37e23260b81945e51.poster.avif?t=1774464132\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/c7128b21159c98a37e23260b81945e51.webm?t=1774464132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/c7128b21159c98a37e23260b81945e51.mp4?t=1774464132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚔️ Face Powerful Bosses</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each biome hides a powerful entity guarding the path forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Massive, unpredictable, and deadly, these bosses will push your reflexes to their limits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/5972bcf6005e32c37cf04dbba368cbd8.poster.avif?t=1774464132\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/5972bcf6005e32c37cf04dbba368cbd8.webm?t=1774464132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/5972bcf6005e32c37cf04dbba368cbd8.mp4?t=1774464132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏆 Climb the Leaderboards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete against players worldwide! Your ranking is based on <strong>survival time, world level, and XP collected</strong>. Can you go further than anyone else?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/4bd88669576092daef174d113ccac348.avif?t=1774464132\" width=600 height=258 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔮 Uncover the Mystery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something is watching the simulation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress deeper, fragments of a hidden story begin to emerge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What lies beyond the final gate?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/d9785ec3853c0392b44ccec33c64e9b3.poster.avif?t=1774464132\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/d9785ec3853c0392b44ccec33c64e9b3.webm?t=1774464132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/d9785ec3853c0392b44ccec33c64e9b3.mp4?t=1774464132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge, adapt, and push your limits in <strong>Glow Journey</strong>! How far will you go? 🔮</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to embark on a new journey, test your reflexes and climb the levels! In this fast-paced survival game, you control a glowing orb, navigating through a mysterious, ever-changing world filled with <strong>dangerous obstacles and relentless enemies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/00d86eee174ba22688c692ca9c52691f.avif?t=1774464132\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🚀 A Thrilling and Evolving Challenge</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level is a challenge to the exit portal, but reaching it won’t be easy! Collect XP orbs to level up and choose from <strong>powerful upgrades</strong>, including passive boosts and unique spells to enhance your survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/901c2df80938f68096e3f8ae970ecaed.poster.avif?t=1774464132\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/901c2df80938f68096e3f8ae970ecaed.webm?t=1774464132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3608390/extras/901c2df80938f68096e3f8ae970ecaed.mp4?t=1774464132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚡ No Attacks, Only Pure Evasion</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There’s no fighting back, only your skills and instincts will keep you alive! The further you go, the <strong>tougher the enemies, the trickier the paths, and the faster your decisions must be</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" aut